 Se tlamantli tlen Harry moiljuiyaya nesiyaya ipan ixko, pampa Lupin kiijtok,
¿Tlake mitstekipachoua, Harry?
 “Axtle,” Harry istlakati. Kiijik se kentsi te uan kiitak nopa Grindylow ki tlachiliyaya ika se imajpil.
“Kema,” kiijtok nimantsi, kitlalik i te ipan imesa Lupin. “Ta tijmati nopa tonali ti tlateuiyayaj
nopa Boggart?”
 “Kema,” kiijtok Lupin ika tlaseuilistli.
 “¿Kenke ax tinechkauili ma nij tlateui?” kiijtok Harry nimantsi.
 Lupin kiketski ixayak.
 “Nimoiljuiskia nopa eliyaya nelia, Harry,” kiijtok, nesiyaya kej mosentlachilijtoya.
 Harry, katli kichiayaya Lupin ma kiijto amo nelia tlen kichijtoya, mosentlachilik.
 "Paratle?" kiijtok sempa.
 “Kuali,” kiijtok Lupin, se kentsi kiixtlapacho, “nimoiljuiyaya tlaj nopa Boggart mitsixnamikiskia, moiljuiskia
iixkopinkayo ​​Lord Voldemort.”
 Harry tlachiayaya. Ax san ya ni eliyaya nopa tlami tlajtoli tlen kichiayaya, nojkia Lupin kiijtok tlen Voldemort
toka. San se maseuali tlen Harry kikakiyaya kiijtouayaya nopa itoka ika chikaualistli (san ya) eliyaya
Tlamachtijketl Dumbledore.
